
---

## **Put this into `.gitignore`**

```gitignore
# Virtual environment
.venv/
venv/

# Python cache
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd

# Notebook checkpoints
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Test/cache tooling
.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.mypy_cache/

# OS/editor files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/

# Data files
data/raw/*
data/processed/*
data/external/*

# Keep folder structure
!data/raw/.gitkeep
!data/processed/.gitkeep
!data/external/.gitkeep